@page "/privacy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy - HireKarlo</PageTitle>

<div class="privacy-page">
    <div class="privacy-container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</p>

        <section>
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to HireKarlo ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your personal information 
                and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard 
                your information when you use our AI-powered career platform.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

            <h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, and password when you register</li>
                <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Resume, skills, work experience, education, and career preferences</li>
                <li><strong>OAuth Data:</strong> When you sign in with Google or LinkedIn, we receive your name, email, and profile picture</li>
                <li><strong>Job Preferences:</strong> Dream companies, target roles, location preferences</li>
                <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Messages sent through our AI chat feature</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Device information (browser type, operating system)</li>
                <li>Usage data (pages visited, features used)</li>
                <li>IP address and approximate location</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide AI-powered resume analysis and optimization</li>
                <li>Match you with relevant job opportunities</li>
                <li>Generate personalized learning paths and career roadmaps</li>
                <li>Conduct mock interviews and provide feedback</li>
                <li>Send job alerts and career recommendations (with your consent)</li>
                <li>Improve our services and develop new features</li>
                <li>Communicate with you about your account and our services</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. AI and Data Processing</h2>
            <p>
                HireKarlo uses artificial intelligence to analyze resumes, match jobs, and provide career guidance. 
                Your data may be processed by:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Groq AI:</strong> For natural language processing and career advice</li>
                <li><strong>HuggingFace:</strong> For text embeddings and similarity matching</li>
                <li><strong>Azure OpenAI:</strong> For advanced AI features (when configured)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                We do not sell your personal data to third parties. AI processing is done solely to provide 
                you with better career recommendations.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We may share your information with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Cloud hosting (Render), database services, and AI providers</li>
                <li><strong>With Your Consent:</strong> When you explicitly choose to share your profile with employers</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>We never auto-submit job applications on your behalf.</strong> All applications require your explicit action.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
            <p>
                We implement appropriate security measures including:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Encryption of data in transit (HTTPS/TLS)</li>
                <li>Secure password hashing</li>
                <li>JWT-based authentication</li>
                <li>Regular security updates</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
                <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct inaccurate information</li>
                <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your account and data</li>
                <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Export your data in a readable format</li>
                <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
            <p>
                We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. 
                We do not use third-party tracking cookies for advertising purposes.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p>
                Our platform may contain links to external job boards and company career pages. 
                We are not responsible for their privacy practices.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>
                HireKarlo is not intended for users under 16 years of age. 
                We do not knowingly collect data from children.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any 
                material changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@hirekarlo.com</li>
                <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/K-riti/HireKarlo" target="_blank">github.com/K-riti/HireKarlo</a></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .privacy-page {
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: var(--bg-primary, #0f0f23);
    }

    .privacy-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(30, 30, 60, 0.6), rgba(20, 20, 40, 0.8));
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 3rem;
        color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .privacy-container h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: #94a3b8;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .privacy-container section {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .privacy-container h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #c4b5fd;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-container h3 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #a5b4fc;
        margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-container p {
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .privacy-container ul {
        margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .privacy-container li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .privacy-container strong {
        color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .privacy-container a {
        color: #06b6d4;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .privacy-container a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .privacy-container {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .privacy-container h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }
    }
</style>
